c: 33
v: 4
t: "Mulungusadalengemitimaiwirim’chifuwachamunthu, ndipo Iye sadalenge akazi anu amene mumawasudzula chifukwa chakuti amalingana ndi amayi anu, ndipo sadawalenge ana omwe mkazi wanu adabereka ndi mwamuna wina kukhala ana anu enieni. Zimenezo ndizo zongokamba zanu chabe koma Mulungu ali kukuuzani inu choonadi ndipo Iye amalangiza njira yoyenera"